+## Definitions
+
+### Cocones under sequential diagrams
+
+```agda
+module _
+  { l1 l2 : Level} (A : sequential-diagram l1) (X : UU l2)
+  where
+
+  cocone-sequential-diagram : UU (l1 ‚äî l2)
