+## Idea
+
+A **sequential diagram** `(A, a)` is a [sequence](foundation.sequences.md) of
+types `A : ‚Ñï ‚Üí ùì§` over the natural numbers, equipped with a family of maps
+`a‚Çô : A‚Çô ‚Üí A‚Çô‚Çä‚ÇÅ` for all `n`.
